data.meta_description: The Warner Recorded Music family includes the worlds most acclaimed artists and labels, with some of the most successful and influential recordings.
data.text:
Recorded Music

Where Originality Finds The Power To Move The World

Our Recorded Music arm includes many of the worlds most visionary artists and labels  from emerging local talent to international superstars, from start-up indies to iconic majors such as Atlantic, 300 Elektra Entertainment, Parlophone, and Warner Records. Our rich catalog boasts some of the most influential recordings in music history, while our innovative teams create a universe of opportunity for our talent to reach fans everywhere.
